  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with recent diagnosis and treatment of a brain tumor will complete a short
      questionnaire concerning the patient's quality of life and emotional state since receiving
      treatment. Caregivers will complete a one-page questionnaire concerning the patient's quality
      of life and emotional state since receiving treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
